summary: New preset built for a computer with a GT 650M.
descriptionHtml:
[size=5][b]PERFORMANCE FRIENDLY ENB
[/b][/size]This preset was designed for my laptop, but I went to lengths to ensure that it still looked phenomenal while keeping 30+ fps on my subpar laptop.
This preset uses anamorphic bloom, something often not used in most ENBs. I've designed this to look fairly cinematic while leaving room for, you know, actually playing the game.

[size=5]INSTALLATION
[/size]Download ENB v0.262
Drop contents of ENB zip into Skyrim Folder
Download my mod
Drop contents of my zip into Skyrim Folder, overwrite anything that comes up.
author: Colonel Mitche1
